import { render } from "@testing-library/react"; import React, { Fragment } from "react"; import Title from "./title"; import Card from "./card"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import "./home.css"; class Home extends React.Component { render() { return (
<div className="card-group text-center mt-5 "> <div className="mx-1"> <Link to="/about"> <Card section="About" text="Something about my personal life" /> </Link> </div> <div className="mx-1"> <Link to="/Knowledge"> <Card section="Knowledge" text="My knowledge from new tecnologies" /> </Link> </div> <div className="mx-1"> <Link to="/education"> <Card section="Education" text="My experience and learnig achademys" /> </Link> </div> <div className="mx-1"> <Link to="/contact"> <Card section="Contact" text="Social Media to contact and chat me!" /> </Link> </div> {/* <Link to="/projects"> <Card section="Projects" text="Personal projects running for test" /> </Link> */} </div> </div> </Fragment> ); } } export default Home;
